project_info:
Our ingredients
We choose only the freshest raw materials, carefully selected according to a sustainable sourcing and a great attention to their quality.

Our Suppliers: A Relationship based on Trust
Ferrero has always preferred to establish direct long-term relationships with producers and suppliers of raw materials based on dialogue, transparency and trust. We collaborate closely with our suppliers to ensure excellent-quality production and freshness of raw materials by testing and processing supervision. We work together to keep the promise we made to our consumers, a promise we also intend to keep in the future: a unique product.

A 50-Year long passion
Love, passion, dedication and great care are the ingredients you will always find in every Nutella® jar, because we love Nutella® as much as our consumers do.
For this reason, we want to give them only the best, as we have been doing since the very beginning.
project_abstract: Nutella is a brand of sweetened hazelnut cocoa spread manufactured by the Italian company Ferrero, that was first introduced in 1965, although its first iteration dates to 1963.
